    • Method Detail

      • setDeferImport

        public HistoryMigrationSpec.Builder setDeferImport(java.lang.Boolean deferImport)
        Defines how vCenter history will be migrated. If set to true, vCenter history will be migrated separately after successful upgrade or migration, otherwise it will be migrated along with core data during the upgrade or migration process. This property was added in vSphere API 6.7. If null, vCenter historical data won't be deferred and will be migrated along with core data.
        Parameters:
        deferImport - New value for the property.
